</style>



  
<div class="container vertical-divider ">

  <div class="column three-sixth">
    <div class='header_2'>Sendai Framework Target A</div>
    <p>Please record in this section human losses (in number of people) needed for Target A, Number of deaths and missing persons attributed to disaster. These fields will be used to compute Indicators A2, A3, B2, B5 and others. If possible, enter disaggregated figures and use the &Sigma; 
    button to calculate the sum of each subgroup</p>  
  </div>
</div>

